-~~~**`-`-* Python OSX Voice Alarm Clock *-'-'**~~~-

Author:  Brian "bojo" Jones
Email:  mojobojo@gmail.com

Reports the designated weather and Google calendar events for the day
using the builtin OSX speech service.

Ideally run this in a crontab as an alarm clock!

Requires the following python modules:
  - Google's gdata : http://code.google.com/p/gdata-python-client/downloads/list
  - pywapi : http://code.google.com/p/python-weather-api/